Package com.sponsorpay.publisher.mbe

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    SPBrandEngageClientStatusListener  
    SPBrandEngageRequestListener
    Interface to be implemented by listeners notified of the results of a SponsorPay BrandEngage request.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    SPBrandEngageActivity
    One-stop-shop class that handles and is responsible for showing a MBE engagement.
    SPBrandEngageClient
    Provides methods to request and show BrandEngage offers and notifies its listener SPBrandEngageClientStatusListener of changes in the status of the engagement.
    SPBrandEngageRequest
    Wrapper calls to perform a BrandEngage request and to notify a SPBrandEngageClientStatusListener of the result
  • Enum Summary

    SPBrandEngageOffersStatus
    The BrandEngage client internal status
